    <tags>pdf pdf-editor pdf-tools stirling-pdf document</tags>
    <summary>Locally hosted web application for viewing and manipulating PDFs</summary>
    <description>Stirling PDF is a robust, locally hosted, web-based PDF manipulation tool offering a wide range of operations — merge, split, convert, compress, OCR, watermark, and more — all running on your own machine.

This package installs the Windows desktop build of Stirling PDF.

Project: https://github.com/Stirling-Tools/Stirling-PDF</description>
